<pre>
タイトル: <font size = 5>PoS BRD2</font>
<b>投稿者　: </b>政景＠鬼兜．E'ci
<!-- ドメイン: 165.76.22.157 -->
URL　　 : 未登録
登録時間:2001年6月17日14時11分</pre>
本文:
<center>
<table width="95%">
<tr bgcolor="#000042"><td>
You say, 'I choose Clarisa.'<BR>
Cilin Spellsinger says 'Take this book of songs and read it.  When you are <BR>
finished, hand it back to me and I will summon sweet Clarisa to test you. <BR>
<BR>
Cilin Spellsinger から The Flute を受け取り、返します。<BR>
<BR>
Cilin Spellsinger says 'Farewell. <BR>
Clarisa Spiritsong says 'Rejoice and sing my friend. <BR>
<BR>
Clarisa Spiritsong が現われ、Cilin Spellsinger が消えました。<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'Hail Clarisa Spiritsong'<BR>
Clarisa Spiritsong says 'Hi there, Xxxxxx !  I give three sections of the <BR>
test of songs, Denise does the rest.  Do you wish to take the test of <BR>
pitch, voice, or tone? <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'I choose pitch'<BR>
Clarisa Spiritsong says 'The pitch that we sing and play has a great effect <BR>
on those who listen.  Keep this in mind, Xxxxxx , and you shall always be <BR>
welcome in taverns and inns.  Now, I need you to return to me a phosphoric <BR>
globe, a shimmering diamond, and a crude wooden flute. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'I choose voice'<BR>
Clarisa Spiritsong says 'The sweet sounds rising forth from our throats are <BR>
what make us truly great.  Go forth and give voice to your songs, and <BR>
return to me a platinum disc, a music box, and a light woolen mantle.  If <BR>
you do this, I shall give you the mantle of the songweaver.  Good luck! <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'I choose tone'<BR>
Clarisa Spiritsong says 'Tone is important to all singers.  Prove to me <BR>
that you can keep your tone even and pure by bringng me an ochre tessera, a <BR>
songbird statuette, and a light woolen mask.  If you do this, I will give <BR>
you the mask of song.
